Privacy Policy
This privacy policy applies to the MyCorn app (hereinafter referred to as "Application") for mobile devices, created by Nahuel Rios (hereinafter referred to as "Service Provider") as a free service. This service is intended for use AS IS.

Information Collection and Use
The Application collects information when you download and use it. This information may include:

Your device's Internet Protocol address (e.g., IP address).
Pages visited within the Application, time and date of visits, and time spent on those pages.
Operating system used on your mobile device.
Advertising identifiers (e.g., Google Advertising ID).
This data is used to provide a better user experience, improve the Application, and show relevant advertisements. The Application does not collect precise location data.

Third-Party Services
The Application uses third-party services that may collect data to identify you. These services include:

Google Play Services
AdMob (for advertisements)
You can review the privacy policies of these providers to learn more about their practices:

Google Play Services Privacy Policy
AdMob Privacy Policy
AdMob and Advertisements
The Application integrates AdMob to display ads. AdMob may collect and use device information, such as advertising identifiers, to serve personalized or non-personalized ads.

Personalized Ads:
AdMob may use your data (e.g., browsing behavior) to display ads tailored to your interests. This is subject to your consent where required by law.

Opting Out of Personalized Ads:
If you prefer not to see personalized ads:

Go to your device's Settings.
Navigate to Privacy > Ads (on Android) or Tracking (on iOS).
Enable the option to Opt-out of Ads Personalization (Android) or Limit Ad Tracking (iOS).
Opt-Out Rights
You can stop all collection of information by uninstalling the Application. Use the standard uninstall processes available on your mobile device or through your application marketplace.

Data Retention Policy
The Service Provider retains user-provided data as long as the Application is installed on your device. If you'd like to delete your data, please contact us at nahuel.rios.bsas@gmail.com, and we will respond promptly.

Children
The Application does not knowingly collect data from children under 13 years of age. If you believe a child has provided personal information, please contact us immediately at nahuel.rios.bsas@gmail.com so we can take appropriate action.

Security
The Service Provider takes precautions to safeguard your data. However, no method of electronic storage is 100% secure, and the Service Provider cannot guarantee absolute security.

Changes to This Policy
This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Changes will be posted on this page. You are advised to review it regularly for updates.

Contact Us
If you have questions or concerns about this policy, please contact us at nahuel.rios.bsas@gmail.com.
